<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>QueueLess | Hospital Queue Management</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* Landing Page Extensions */
    .landing-wrapper {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .hero-h1 {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--primary);
      letter-spacing: -2px;
    }

    .hero-p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .btn-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .landing-card {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
      width: 300px;
      transition: 0.3s;
      border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    }

    .landing-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      border-color: var(--primary);
    }

    .landing-card i {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: block;
    }

    .landing-card h3 {
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: var(--text-main);
    }

    .landing-card p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      .features {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .btn-group {
        flex-direction: column;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 300px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="landing-wrapper">
    <div style="text-align: center; animation: slideUp 0.8s ease-out;">
      <h1 class="hero-h1"><i class="fas fa-wave-square" style="color: var(--accent);"></i> QueueLess</h1>
      <p class="hero-p">Experience the future of clinical efficiency. Minimizing wait times, maximizing patient care.
        Join the wait-free revolution today.</p>

      <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="/login" class="button"
          style="text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; padding: 18px 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; border-radius: 100px;">
          <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Access Dashboard
        </a>
        <a href="/signup" class="button"
          style="text-decoration: none; background: white; color: var(--primary); border: 2px solid var(--primary); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px; padding: 18px 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; border-radius: 100px;">
          <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> New Account
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features" style="display: flex; gap: 30px; animation: slideUp 1s ease-out;">
      <div class="landing-card">
        <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
        <h3>For Providers</h3>
        <p>Streamline patient intake, monitor the waiting room in real-time, and focus on delivering care.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="landing-card">
        <i class="fas fa-clock-rotate-left"></i>
        <h3>For Patients</h3>
        <p>Register from anywhere, track your position live, and only arrive when it's your turn.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="landing-card">
        <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
        <h3>Efficiency First</h3>
        <p>Built with modern web standards to ensure lightning-fast performance and reliable queue tracking.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>

</html>